<body><!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>About Us - SafeNest</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="about.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
        </header>
    
        <main class="about-section">
            <section class="intro">
                <p>Welcome to <strong>SafeNest!</strong> Our mission is to create a safe, supportive, and empowering online space dedicated to teenage girls' health, safety, and personal growth. We aim to be a trusted source of information and guidance, helping young women navigate challenges confidently and thrive as they grow.</p>
            </section>
    
            <section class="who-we-are">
                <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                <p>SafeNest was founded by a team passionate about empowering young women. Recognizing the unique challenges that teenage girls face in today’s world, we developed SafeNest to be more than just a resource—it’s a community of support, where girls can find reliable advice, insightful articles, and real-time guidance whenever they need it.</p>
            </section>
    
            <section class="mission-vision">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is simple: to nurture, support, and guide teenage girls as they grow. We’re dedicated to offering the tools, insights, and encouragement necessary to foster self-confidence, resilience, and maturity.</p>
    
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>We envision a world where every girl feels empowered to pursue her goals, secure in her health, safety, and self-worth. SafeNest aims to be the leading platform where young women can find answers, cope with difficult situations, and receive the support they need to achieve their dreams.</p>
            </section>
    
            <section class="values">
                <h2>Our Values</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Empathy</strong> – Understanding and caring for our users in all their unique experiences.</li>
                    <li><strong>Empowerment</strong> – Helping young women make informed decisions and take control of their lives.</li>
                    <li><strong>Safety</strong> – Creating a trusted, secure environment where users can feel comfortable seeking help.</li>
                    <li><strong>Support</strong> – Providing reliable and relevant information, tools, and resources to guide every step of the way.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
    
            <section class="offer">
                <h2>What We Offer</h2>
                <p>SafeNest offers a variety of resources and tools tailored for teenage girls:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Healthcare Guidance</strong> – Access to health tips, mental wellness tools, and support for managing physical and emotional well-being.</li>
                    <li><strong>Safety Support</strong> – Crisis response tools, including real-time guidance for emergencies and tips on staying safe online and offline.</li>
                    <li><strong>Personal Growth Resources</strong> – Articles, exercises, and AI-driven recommendations that promote self-awareness, confidence, and personal development.</li>
                    <li><strong>Community Connection</strong> – A safe and inclusive space for teenage girls to find support, inspiration, and connection with like-minded peers.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
    
            <section class="team">
                <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
                <p>Behind SafeNest is a team of professionals from diverse backgrounds, including health experts, tech developers, and advocates for women’s empowerment. We’re here to build an inclusive community where teenage girls can find answers, guidance, and encouragement in a way that’s respectful and uplifting.</p>
            </section>
    
            <section class="join">
                <h2>Join Us on Our Journey</h2>
                <p>SafeNest is committed to ongoing improvement and expansion of our resources to better serve our users. We welcome feedback, ideas, and questions from our community—because SafeNest is a place that grows with you.</p>
            </section>
        </main>
